name: Queen Amidala (AI)
Lore: 'Leader. Amidala was only twelve when she was elected Princess of Theed. Now at age fourteen, she is Naboo''s Queen, and the savior of her planet.',
Text: 'Deploys -1 to Naboo. Amidala and your other Republic characters present are defense value +2, and immune to You Are Beaten, Sniper, and attrition < 3.',
